body:
This seems intentional, but I don't understand the intention.

In https://tour.golang.org/static/css/app.css, both the normal
color and text-decoration properties of a elements are suppressed:
a {
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
}

/cc: @campoy, this change is made in the tour redesign commit.
https://github.com/golang/tour/commit/4d282f83d3f705f38e724c60a36f48680e90a71e
